ly but remained a strong contender atParis 2024.\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He won gold in Tokyo, running 43.85secs to beat out Anthony Zambrano and Kirani James.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 825, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 754, \"end\": 759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9907460256374672, \"rank\": 0.009196044359836873, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 791, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Zambrano\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anthony Zambrano\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Zambrano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Zambrano\"}, {\"begin\": 812, \"end\": 818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirani\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kirani\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirani\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirani\"}, {\"begin\": 819, \"end\": 824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"score\": 0.547304501974558, \"rank\": 0.8242814487594704, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gardiner pulled up injured in his World Championship 400m semi-final in Budapest last year.\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 827, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Gardiner\", \"score\": 0.9991812939841304, \"rank\": 0.00044477723523654946, \"text\": \"Gardiner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Gardiner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource